# Oiorest zone exporter
Python script to export the zones from geo.oiorest.dk/takstzoner.json to graphml. One file per operator.

Requires networkx.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
tagline: Gets all public transport zones in Denmark from geo.oiorest.dk
name: Oiorest-zone-miner
